@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

actor User
participant "Next.js UI\n(index.tsx)" as UI
participant "AWS AppSync\n(GraphQL API)" as AppSync
participant "publishToSNS\nResolver" as SNSResolver
participant "saveToDynamodb\nResolver" as DynamoResolver
participant "translateMessage\nResolver" as TranslateResolver
participant "AWS SNS" as SNS
participant "AWS DynamoDB" as DynamoDB
participant "AWS Translate" as Translate

== Initialization ==
User -> UI: Load Application
activate UI
UI -> AppSync: Subscribe to OnPlusOne
activate AppSync
AppSync --> UI: Subscription Active
UI -> AppSync: Query getTotals
AppSync --> UI: Return Current Vote Counts
deactivate AppSync
deactivate UI

== Vote Submission ==
User -> UI: Select Country (BR/CM)\nand Message
activate UI
User -> UI: Click Vote Button
UI -> AppSync: Mutation AddVote(VoteInput)
activate AppSync

AppSync -> SNSResolver: Pipeline Step 1:\nPublish Vote Event
activate SNSResolver
SNSResolver -> SNS: Publish Vote Message
activate SNS
SNS --> SNSResolver: Event Published
deactivate SNS
SNSResolver --> AppSync: Continue Pipeline
deactivate SNSResolver

AppSync -> DynamoResolver: Pipeline Step 2:\nSave Vote Data
activate DynamoResolver
DynamoResolver -> DynamoDB: PutItem(Vote)
activate DynamoDB
DynamoDB --> DynamoResolver: Vote Saved
deactivate DynamoDB
DynamoResolver --> AppSync: Continue Pipeline
deactivate DynamoResolver

AppSync -> TranslateResolver: Pipeline Step 3:\nTranslate Message
activate TranslateResolver
TranslateResolver -> Translate: Translate to English
activate Translate
Translate --> TranslateResolver: Translated Message
deactivate Translate
TranslateResolver --> AppSync: Return Vote with Translation
deactivate TranslateResolver

AppSync --> UI: AddVote Response (Vote)
deactivate AppSync
UI --> User: Display Vote Confirmation
deactivate UI

== Real-time Update Broadcast ==
AppSync -> UI: OnPlusOne Subscription:\nNew Vote Event
activate UI
UI -> UI: Update Vote Count
UI -> UI: Update Timeline
UI --> User: Display Updated Results
deactivate UI

@enduml
